{
  "page": "Pyramid of Naqqan",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><p>The <b>pyramid of Naqqan</b> is the seat of the <a href=\"/index.php/House_of_Naqqan\" title=\"House of Naqqan\">House of Naqqan</a> in <a href=\"/index.php/Meereen\" title=\"Meereen\">Meereen</a>. The <a href=\"/index.php/Pyramid\" title=\"Pyramid\">pyramid</a> is green and black in color and is located near the <a href=\"/index.php/Pyramid_of_Pahl\" title=\"Pyramid of Pahl\">pyramid of Pahl</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Radwd52.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Radwd52.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Pyramid_of_Naqqan&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: References\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"references-small\">\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-Radwd52.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-Radwd52.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Dance_with_Dragons\" title=\"A Dance with Dragons\">A Dance with Dragons</a></i>, <a href=\"/index.php/A_Dance_with_Dragons-Chapter_52\" title=\"A Dance with Dragons-Chapter 52\">Chapter 52</a>, Daenerys IX.</span>\n</li>\n</ol></div></div>\n\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260404210419\nCache expiry: 1209600\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.010 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.011 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 83/1000000\nPreprocessor generated node count: 8534/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 441/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 22/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 8/